Perceptor/Peceptor's team/Darkfate::

Perceptor leaded the group towards Darkfate's base. Soon they arrived 
and, Perceptor used his com link and said "We come back.."

"Excellent" answered Darkfate by comm link "Alarms are turned off and 
the bridge will be ready soon"

"As soon as the bridge appear" said Perceptor to Starscream "We'll be 
in Darkfate's base"

The bridge appeared and soon Perceptor and his team are walking 
towards Darkfate's base.
